The '''rufous-bellied triller''' ('''''Lalage aurea''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Campephagidae]].
It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[North Maluku]] in Indonesia. Its natural [[habitat]]s are [[Subtropics|subtropical]] or [[Tropics|tropical]] moist lowland [[forest]]s and subtropical or tropical mangrove forests.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Rufous-bellied Triller - eBird |url=https://ebird.org/species/rubtri1 |access-date=2024-05-16 |website=ebird.org |language=en}}</ref>

